	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here are a few upgrades for you Lonaleb...<br><br>Hardened Kodiak Leather Bracer - I hunted for this myself at level 35. They drop off of A Tundra Kodiak in Eastern Wastes, Feral Cave Kodiak in Great Divide, Ferocious Cave Kodiak in Great Divide or Savage Cave Kodiak in Great Divide. Or can be bought for under 100pp.<br><br>Crown of the Froglok Kings - this drops in Lower Guk from none other than the Froglok King. Or can be bought for about 1000pp.<br><br>Acrylia Reinforced Mantle - Can be bought from your local tailor. I think i bought mine for 650pp.<br><br>Spore Covered Tunic - This drops off of A Fungoid Sporeling, A Fungoid, or A Mature Fungoid all in the Netherbian Lair. I used this until I bought my Acrylia Reinforced Tunic. I maxed my FD for level 20 and went to Netherbian Lair and easily scored this tunic as well as all the other pieces of Spore Armor in about 4 hours. Or can be bought for about 50-75pp. This is the same AC as your LockJaw Vest but less than 1/3rd the weight (Vest is 1.5, Spore Tunic is 0.4).<br><br>Spore Covered Leggings - As a firm believer in AC&gt;anything, These pants have One more AC than your Wu's but you will lose the AGI from the Wu's and gain minimal Save to cold (2SVCold) with Spore Covered. This &quot;upgrade&quot; all depends on how you feel personally about AGI points. If I remember correctly, 4 points of AGI = 1 AC but I may be wrong.<br>Gatorscale Leggings are also an option. I camped these myself as well instead of paying for them. These are 7AC 4WIS 15HP and drop off of An Ancient Croc in Upper Guk. They can be bought for about 400-500pp.<br><br>Other than that, for the amount of plat you say you have at the time, what you have is great stuff. What I tend to do at my current level (40) is to look at the higher level monks on this board who have setup Magelo Profiles. Master Keyeluke is a perfect example. I am buying my gear directly from looking at his Magelo profile. If he made it to level 60 with his gear, I should be able to do the same. Of course, there are some pieces he has that either, 1. I can not afford, or 2. I am not high enough level to attain yet, but I acquire the pieces I am able to.<br>Also, keep in mind prices vary from server to server. The prices I listed may not jive with your server.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Jul 23 11:52:18 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Ssalizka Sss'ra<br>44 Iksar Monk<br>Vazaelle <br> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286441" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286441</a></td></tr>
